- cs.GR (Graphics) is relevant as the paper deals with the creation of images on a canvas.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper discusses the interaction between human painters and AI algorithms.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with the creation of multimedia art using AI algorithms.
